    passage:`<p style="font-weight:700;font-size:15.5px;margin-bottom:10px">Eastview Hotel — Guest Satisfaction Survey Results</p>
<p style="font-size:15px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:9px">We are pleased to share the results of our most recent guest satisfaction survey, conducted in September. A total of 842 guests completed the survey, representing a response rate of 34 percent — our highest since we began conducting annual surveys five years ago.</p>
<p style="font-size:15px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:9px">Overall guest satisfaction reached 91 percent, an increase of four percentage points compared to last year. The highest-rated areas were cleanliness (96%), staff friendliness (94%), and room comfort (92%). The lowest-rated area was parking convenience, which received a satisfaction score of 67 percent.</p>
<p style="font-size:15px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:9px">Based on this feedback, we will be expanding our parking facilities starting in January. We will also introduce a new valet parking service to address guests' concerns more immediately.</p>
<p style="font-size:15px;line-height:2">We thank all guests who participated in the survey. Your feedback helps us continuously improve the Eastview experience.</p>`,
